# Figma Atomic Component Composition

- Canonical composition policy now lives in `figma-slot-composition-hard-gate`.
- Use this note only as supplemental guidance for compound families such as `Tabs`, segmented controls, menus, accordions, or steppers.
- Mirror code composition in Figma, keep child axes on the child, and keep parent axes on the parent.
